# Safe to commit: token is read from the environment (never put a literal PAT here).
# Before `pnpm install`: export GH_TOKEN=<PAT with read:packages>
# Or add that export to ~/.zshrc / Keychain-backed shell init (outside this repo).
@ctxpipe-ai:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GH_TOKEN}
